		{
			"id": "chk-p0p1",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 0–1**\n\n☑ Concept freeze D1–D12\n☑ Research brief + roadmap\n☑ Free NIM pins + pin log\n☑ Docker smoke\n☑ Pre-reg experiment YAML\n☑ Phase 1 research package",
			"x": 50,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 620,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p2",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 2 — Paper organism**\n\n☑ Episode runner + SQLite\n☑ Frozen multi-seed fitness\n☑ Weight checkpoints (`seo weights`)\n☑ Mutation accept / reject loop\n☑ Ablation B0 / Bw / Bc / Bcw + δ report\n☑ Evolve schedule / plateau\n☑ Docker-isolated candidate eval\n☑ Hardened Docker (caps, non-root, RO job)\n☑ Schema AST + adversarial tests\n☑ Runs/ lab note\n\n☐ **δ success** Bcw ≥ B0+δ\n   (open — live δ = −2.51)",
			"x": 720,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 660,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p3",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 3 — Free LLM pool + critic**\n\n☑ Pins: coder / critic / summarizer\n☑ Critic taxonomy + mutation gate\n☑ Router + session budgets\n☑ Summarizer episode distill\n☑ `seo metrics` rollup\n☑ `seo critic-ab` offline A/B\n☑ Live free-NIM field trial\n☑ Mutation memory (SQL lessons)\n☑ Schema contracts (ticks / choice weights)\n\n☐ Soft critic `other` / more code accepts\n☐ δ claim under free NIM still open",
			"x": 1430,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 660,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p4",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 4 — Observer UI**\n\n☐ Population / organism list\n☐ Lineage tree\n☐ Mutation inspector\n☐ Event timeline\n☐ Kill switch / pause / freeze\n\n**Phase 5–6**\n\n☐ Multi-organism population\n☐ Research-grade hardening\n☐ Longer experiments",
			"x": 2140,
			"y": 880,
			"width": 600,
			"height": 560,
			"color": "1"
		},

